{"tid":864423,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今次發硬達 幣少爺話打飛機可以賺錢","createTime":"2018-10-16T07:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T14:38:40.000Z","uid":43683,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1003a9560dedba58cc3f6234a3effa426126e982","tid":864423,"uid":43683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"由暗網生成既成人網站 其實己經有測試版出左<br />\n<br />\n所以正式黎講 成個線上打飛機網己經係運作緊<br />\n<br />\n由我團隊開發既錢包app 白皮書 智能合約兌換亦將會係11月7號之前公佈哂出黎<br />\n<br />\n咁一定會有人問 點解上網打飛機都有錢收？<br />\n<br />\n錢從何來 ？<br />\n<br />\n其實有幾點可以保證收益既<br />\n<br />\n包括廣告商 <br />\n幣價升值<br />\n抵押品 當然我仲有絕招唔講出黎住<br />\n<br />\n大家拭目以待 睇住mv欣賞下先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Epoch.Cryptocurrency/videos/261522137897944/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEpoch.Cryptocurrency%2Fvideos%2F261522137897944%2F&d=4ca4e27lY2GGV30PmgtKiKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=dc27586e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Epoch.Cryptocurrency/videos/261522137897944/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次無得輸啦 每日打幾個飛機好快就有錢過李+x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf24cc9a6dc1cbc260a72ce9ec318df24ba55b1","tid":864423,"uid":43683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:43:27.000Z","msg":"斃家伙 唔記得set member<br />\n益埋D CD ROM<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa1d4d7740acf8d5af1222e9e396e157a720d19","tid":864423,"uid":11448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"會唔會睇到CP"},{"pid":"315d86a41e31b608fe5fa7a83dcad8869b9a8314","tid":864423,"uid":73764,"like":1,"